{"address1": "Olympia Terraces, No. 15B(SP)", "address2": "SIDCO Industrial Estate Guindy", "city": "Chennai", "zip": "600032", "country": "India", "phone": "91 44 4252 5300", "website": "https://www.coromandel.biz", "industry": "Agricultural Inputs", "industryKey": "agricultural-inputs", "industryDisp": "Agricultural Inputs", "sector": "Basic Materials", "sectorKey": "basic-materials", "sectorDisp": "Basic Materials", "longBusinessSummary": "Coromandel International Limited provides agriculture solutions in India and internationally. It operates through the Nutrient and Other Allied Business, and Crop Protection segments. The company offers fertilizers, including GroPlus Pro Mg and Gromor Urea Super Phosphate; bio-products comprising MycoRitz and Grovibe; specialty nutrients, such as Pixibud, Pixigrow, Nano Urea, Areca Shakti, and Coffee Bliss; and crop protection products that include Caveco, Marvex, Prachand, Benofit, Rukawat X, Myconil, Eezykil Ultra, Cortus, Victini Z, and Toscee. It also provides value-added services, including drone spraying, soil testing, crop diagnostics, and weather insights, as well as e-commerce platform for advisory and ordering. The company was formerly known as Coromandel Fertilisers Ltd and changed its name to Coromandel International Limited in September 2009. Coromandel International Limited was incorporated in 1961 and is based in Chennai, India. Coromandel International Limited operates as a subsidiary of E.I.D.- Parry (India) Limited.", "fullTimeEmployees": 5540, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Arun  Alagappan", "age": 49, "title": "Executive Chairman", "yearBorn": 1976, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 103113000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. S.  Sankarasubramanian B.Sc, ICWA", "age": 56, "title": "MD, CEO & Additional Director", "yearBorn": 1969, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 44779000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Narayanan  Ve